08-03-2014 Javi Roman <javiroman@redoop.org>

	* Added Kafka and Spark packages for Real Time, aka
	Speed Layer for Lambda Architecture.

	Spark is based in the upstream of BigTop 0.7.0. The
	kafka package is based on the [BIGTOP-989] pull request
	not included in the upstream.

26-02-2014 Javi Roman <javiroman@redoop.org>

	* Change RPM name nomenclature:

	toolName-toolVersion-distroTag_packageVersion.arch.rpm

	Examples:
	flume-1.4.0-openbus0.0.1_1.noarch.rpm
	flume-1.4.0-openbus0.0.1_2.noarch.rpm
	flume-1.4.0-openbus0.0.1_3.noarch.rpm

	hadoop-hdfs-datanode-2.2.0-openbus0.0.1_1.x86_64.rpm

